{"tid":288518,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠基金會續推派錢計劃　新增屯門共4地區萬名DSE生可獲5000元","createTime":"2017-06-18T08:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T15:04:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"085bcd65301f02d63c46be39c95cfb2e165942be","tid":288518,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠基金會指出，去年「善用錢」計劃推出後，深受社會歡迎令學生學會善用金錢，同時收到很多學校、家長及地區人士意見，希望計劃能擴至屯門區中學。「善用錢」2018年的計劃將擴展至屯門區，連原有的離島區、天水圍及元朗地區，共有共91間學校、逾1萬名考生可受惠，有關計劃詳情稍後公布。<br />\n<br />\n基金會向超過5700名去年參與計劃的考生發放問卷，回收的問卷中有7成學生表示將把5000元用於學業相關的用途，如DSE考試費、留位費、購買練習、報讀補習班等，亦有會用於儲蓄、幫補家計、購物及旅行。<br />\n<br />\n基金會續指，部分學生指出該5000元是他們人生中的第一筆金錢，故學懂珍惜、好好利用及規劃，讓5000元成為實踐理想的起步點；更有學生指因為計劃而第一次踏進銀行「開戶口存錢」，認為新體驗非常有意思。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170618/s00001/1497767551644#sthash.JAwHGUaa.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170618%2Fs00001%2F1497767551644%23sthash.JAwHGUaa.dpuf&d=nrLBRfJtwkoYs2ibctHC8KMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=375e7ce6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170618%2Fs00001%2F1497767551644%23sthash.JAwHGUaa.dpuf&h=b5c5d38c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170618/s00001/1497767551644#sthash.JAwHGUaa.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"219e3095238254fae9beb66e54db1374993bf4b8","tid":288518,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"根本地產商先係政府<br />\n交咩費都係畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690b5b6573e87fe94986de96133c464e194e8c55","tid":288518,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T11:24:35.000Z","msg":"屯門元朗先有窮人？"},{"pid":"c5436ae5c9fc270a37c9334e5fad9447e3628e29","tid":2885